	.string "Excuse me, young one.\n"
	.string "Have you good eyesight?\p"
	.string "There is an odd tree past here, and to\n"
	.string "my tired eyes it seems to wiggle.$"

BattleFrontier_OutsideEast_Text_OnceAnOddTreePastHere:
	.string "Excuse me, young one.\n"
